  /**
   * Render the inline AI panel (Pain #2 — sinais IA inline ao avaliar).
   * Reads ai_triage_*, ai_analysis, last_briefing_* from the application object
   * (extended in get_evaluation_form via migration 970000).
   * Default collapsed; expand → 2 columns Sonnet/Gemini side by side.
   * p109 Onda 4 Fase 2: thumbs/override controls (validations array from list_my_ai_validations).
